cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.OS, cs.SY, cs.SE 

The paper discusses vulnerabilities and attacks in the scheduler of virtual machines, which is a critical component of cloud computing systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.OS (Operating Systems), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
